A '''tourist highway''' is a road which is [[marketing|marketed]] as particularly suited for [[tourist]]s. Tourist highways may be formed when existing roads are promoted with [[traffic sign]]s and [[advertising]] material. Some tourist highways are built especially for tourism purposes, others may be former highways replaced by a new [[freeway]] or [[motorway]].
